{"tid":125744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"參觀波音 川普誓言：留住每份工作","createTime":"2017-02-18T17:51:22.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T13:44:02.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"63026703df98c2caa8cb748d8cc5b626be14a26b","tid":125744,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T17:51:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2017/02/18/6/3190500.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2017%2F02%2F18%2F6%2F3190500.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=a63c44a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n川普16日召開上任以來第一場單人記者會。（美聯社）<br />\n自小羅斯福以降的美國歷任總統都愛參觀波音工廠，站在閃閃發亮的新型飛機旁拍照；川普17日也安排這樣的行程，參觀波音南卡羅萊納州組裝廠，吹捧波音787夢幻客機證明美國製造業即將復興，未來會提供更多工廠工作。<br />\n<br />\n但大約五年前，歐巴馬參觀波音位於華盛頓州的組裝廠時，卻傳達出大相逕庭的訊息：美國必須為工廠自動化導致製造業工作流失作好準備，並從而調整經濟結構。<br />\n<br />\n川普將工廠工作的流失怪罪在廉價海外勞力和自貿條約的頭上。他參訪波音工廠時的演說，完全不提組裝線上自動化機器人的角色日益吃重，對波音在聲明中承認，787機隊的零件有30%來自海外工廠也避重就輕。<br />\n<br />\n他說：「美國的目標必須是減少仰賴進口，多倚重美國本土製造的產品。我們會奮力留住美國每一份工作。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/10764/2292468?from=udn-relatednews_ch2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F10764%2F2292468%3Ffrom%3Dudn-relatednews_ch2&d=hgakeblNVNpTjPSl%2FdBGDp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=0d2f4cde\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/10764/2292468?from=udn-relatednews_ch2</a>"},{"pid":"796487e2cab8a70452ec51dc8d54901c4124b379","tid":125744,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-18T18:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbadaf6e482dea5eb122956acd7b1730fc52600","tid":125744,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T02:09:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bac9d571eb181318c86c3909a7b2747892b02d3","tid":125744,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T03:02:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869a3131f476266a39f791eabebeac8437d91e65","tid":125744,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T03:04:45.000Z","msg":"我都參觀過 真係好壯觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇記錯個廠房係全世界最大單一建築物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bc5acff3f53b1782a9bd480e38e2502b0d26a2c","tid":125744,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T03:05:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都參觀過 真係好壯觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n冇記錯個廠房係全世界最大單一建築物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來佢唔係去西雅圖嗰個 自膠"},{"pid":"e4eb6ee7e77f5839fc85380387e8ba75a9f07265","tid":125744,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T03:14:05.000Z","msg":"787嘅機身、部分機翼、機輪、洗Pat馬桶等，都係日本貨 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d504b0ab73baec689e923833fcf6170e782307d4","tid":125744,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}